Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:07.28,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,I want to start our field trip here,\Nin the world famous Canterlot Sculpture Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.26,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,That one over there\Nrepresents friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:15.32,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,All right, my little ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.44,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,This one represents victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:20.11,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,How cool would it be to have\N{\i1}that{\i0} for a cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.66,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:25.12,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If you were actually\Nvictoryful at somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.85,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That's not a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.90,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,What are you? A dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:29.98,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:33.62,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Now this is a really interesting statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.94,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,What do you notice about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.72,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It's got an eagle claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.04,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And a lion paw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:40.41,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And a snake tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.19,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,This creature is called a draconequus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:46.93,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,He is the head of a pony and a body\Nmade up of all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.03,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose that represents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.48,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.42,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:52.20,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.38,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It's not chaos, you dodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.89,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Don't call me things\NI don't know the meaning of!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.78,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And it is too chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:00:59.64,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You're both wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.44,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Actually, in a way you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.49,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,This statue represents discord…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.41,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,…which means a lack of\Nharmony between ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.89,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,In fact, you three have\Ndemonstrated discord so well…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:25.35,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,…that you're each going to\Nwrite me an essay explaining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.13,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Now let's go. And I don't\Nwant any more fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,-It's confusion!\N-Evil!\N-Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:23.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Eeew! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:40.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait a second! It's not supposed\Nto rain until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:41.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You can't just…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey! I didn't tell you to go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:53.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! What's\Ngoing on with that rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I mean… chocolate milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I mean… chocolate milk rain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There's crazy weather\Nall over Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale's getting soaked\Nby a major cola storm right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. I'm not leaving you,\Ntill I get control of Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Why would you wanna stop {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:17.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I heard about your troubles, Applejack,\Nand I came to see if there's anything I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Without getting wet. Or dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.21,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or out from under my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Do somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Now Angel, you really shouldn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No! It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.13,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I must be seeing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:43.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, everyone! I've learned\Na new spell that'll fix everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My fail-safe spell…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…failed! What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,Uh… Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Spike. Twilight will come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Time for Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow! Can you corral all those\Nclouds in one corner of the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack! I need you to bring those\Nhigh strong storm clouds down to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:40.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh dear! I hope that none\Nof the animals see these…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,…delicious chocolate-filled\Ncotton candy clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to have to share them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You and me both, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:56.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And when y'all are done that, feel free\Nto have some popcorn for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You see, Spike? You\Nshould never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:02.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can't\Novercome if we all work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls! Princess Celestia wants\Nto see us all in Canterlot immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia! We came\Nas fast as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:27.13,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twilight. Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is this about the weather?\NAnd the animals' weird behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's happening out there? Why\Nisn't my magic working? Is there…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.32,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.37,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I've called you here\Nfor a matter of great importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.63,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It seems an old foe of mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.91,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…someone I thought I had\Ndefeated long ago, has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:46.10,Celestia,,0,0,0,,His name is Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:50.31,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Discord is the mischievous\Nspirit of disharmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.49,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Before my sister and I\Nstood up to him…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…he ruled Equestria in an eternal state\Nof unrest and unhappiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Luna and I saw how miserable\Nlife was for earth ponies…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.02,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…pegasi and unicorns alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.49,Celestia,,0,0,0,,So after discovering\Nthe Elements of Harmony…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…we combined our powers\Nand rose up against him…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.47,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…turning him to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Alright, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.14,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I thought the spell we cast would\Nkeep him contained forever…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.02,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…but since Luna and I are\Nno longer connected to the Elements…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.08,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…the spell has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No longer connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,This is Canterlot tower, where\Nthe Elements are kept inside…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.12,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…since all of you recovered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:31.66,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I need you to wield the Elements of Harmony\Nonce again and stop Discord…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:35.22,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…before he thrusts\Nall of Equestria into eternal chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But why us? Why don't you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! We're famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.82,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You six showed the full\Npotential of the Elements…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:45.74,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…by harnessing the magic of your\Nfriendship to beat a mighty foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.38,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Although Luna and I\Nonce wielded the Elements…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…it is you, who now control their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.56,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And it is you, who must defeat Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia, you can count on…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.81,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.46,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Eternal chaos comes with\Nchocolate rain, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.31,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,CHOCOLATE RAIN!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to her, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'd be honored to use\Nthe Elements of Harmony again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You can keep the Elements.\NI'll take that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.43,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Have no fear, ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I have total confidence that you\Nwill be able to defeat Discord…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.29,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh well. If anyone needs me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:47.92,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,…I'll be outside in the chocolate\Npuddles with a giant swizzle straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Elements! They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:55.15,Celestia,,0,0,0,,That chamber is protected by\Na powerful spell that only I can break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.16,Celestia,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make sense…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.61,Discord,,0,0,0,,"Make sense"? Oh, what fun\Nis there in making sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.91,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Discord! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.93,Discord,,0,0,0,,Did you miss me, Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.81,Discord,,0,0,0,,I've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:19.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's quite lonely being encased in stone.\NBut you wouldn't know that, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:23.11,Discord,,0,0,0,,Because I don't turn ponies into stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:27.72,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Enough! What have you done\Nwith the Elements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.07,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, I just borrowed them\Nfor a teensy little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You'll never get away\Nwith this, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:39.04,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd forgotten how grim\Nyou can be, Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.53,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's really quite boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey! Nopony insults the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.66,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh! You must be Rainbow Dash…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:53.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,…famed for her loyalty ‒ the Element\Nof Harmony you represent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's right! I'll always\Nbe loyal to the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're wasting our time\Ntalking to a tacky window.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:05.47,Discord,,0,0,0,,The beautiful Rarity, representing\Nthe Element of Generosity…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.32,Discord,,0,0,0,,…if I'm not mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So you know who we are. Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.81,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know much more than\Nthat, honest Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You seem to know our strengths too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.11,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes, Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:21.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,And yours is the most powerful\Nand elusive element ‒ magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:25.54,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's is kindness and Pinkie Pie's\Nis the personal favorite of mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.03,Discord,,0,0,0,,…laughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,He's standing on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.39,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Stop stalling, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.67,Celestia,,0,0,0,,What have you done with\Nthe Elements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.01,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh! So boring, Celestia. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.82,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll tell you, but\NI'll only tell you my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:49.17,Discord,,0,0,0,,To retrieve your missing elements,\Njust make sense of this change of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:52.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns are my master plan…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:55.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,…then find the Elements\Nback where you began.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Can we go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What do you reckon he meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,"Twists and turns" and then\Nthe "back where we started".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I bet Discord hid the Elements\Nin the palace labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.01,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Good luck, my little ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:18.82,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The fate of Equestria is in your hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Princess. We won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We… We have to go in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nope! Dopey Discord\Nforgot about these babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:38.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll just do a quick flyover and\Nwe'll have the Elements in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,My wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.13,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Your horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,My horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:03.09,Discord,,0,0,0,,You… You should see the looks\Non your faces. Priceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Give us our wings and horns back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.67,Discord,,0,0,0,,You'll get them back in good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.10,Discord,,0,0,0,,I simply took them to ensure\Nthere's no cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.79,Discord,,0,0,0,,You see, this is the first\Nrule of our game:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:16.28,Discord,,0,0,0,,No flying and no magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The first rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:22.82,Discord,,0,0,0,,The second rule is: everypony has to play\Nor the game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.98,Discord,,0,0,0,,And I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.91,Discord,,0,0,0,,Good luck, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Never fear, girls. We have each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Like Twilight said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:40.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can't overcome\Nif we all stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All right, girls! Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:50.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stay calm, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everypony head to the middle as fast as\Nyou can and we'll regroup there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,See you in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.01,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,See you guys there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:04.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What's that?! Who's there?! GIIIRLS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Who are y'all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:41.04,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The keepers of the grove of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.66,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You may ask us…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.89,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…a one question:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Past, future or present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.86,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But be warned…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.42,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…that the truth…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…may not always be pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:56.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Alright then. I don't trust\Nthis place for the hill a' beans…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,…but I got a real bad feelin'\Nabout this feller Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What's gonna come of this\Nhere mission we're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:07.46,Somepony,,0,0,0,,For the answer you seek…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.63,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…go ahead! Take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I hope I'll never see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.43,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,-Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,-Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's settled then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:25.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Our friendship… over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:37.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It can't be true. It just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That just can't be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.46,Somepony,,0,0,0,,When all the truth does…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.74,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…is make your heart ache…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:52.93,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…sometimes a lie is easier to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:02.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack! Thank goodness.\NI thought I heard voices over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I was talkin' to, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nopony! Nopony whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:13.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.74,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on. Uh, we best be goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Did Applejack just…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:22.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight.\NApplejack wouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest\Nballoon garden I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's the first balloon garden\NI've ever seen, but still…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey! What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:53.57,Somepony,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Pinkie Pie?\NI thought you appreciated a good laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's different. They're\Nlaughing *at* me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.71,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's hardly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:01.27,Discord,,0,0,0,,Your friends laugh at you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,My friends laugh {\i1}with{\i0} me, not at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.63,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:27.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:30.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,And here I thought\Nlaughter made you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:33.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.77,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:43.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie! Are we glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:46.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You are, huh? WHY? Need a good laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:47.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:52.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose has her\Nso upset? It's not like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice anythin'\Nstrange about Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:16:01.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Weird. Better pick up the pace before\Nthe stress of this gets the better of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:09.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I was expecting an audience with\Nthe Princess, not outdoor sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,Welcome to your lucky day, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:25.83,Discord,,0,0,0,,You've found the one thing in Equestria\Nthat could rival my face for sheer beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:31.16,Discord,,0,0,0,,What do you think? You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:34.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes… I like very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:41.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,NO! No. I shan't succumb\Nto such fabulousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:46.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Must… get to the center…\Nto meet… the others…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,MINE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, Rarity…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It took forever, but it was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:03.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who knew three little gemstones would turn out\Nto be this handsome HUNK of a diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Are we glad to see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why are you carrying\Na humongous boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "boulder"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:26.78,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This big, beautiful, bedazzling\Nrock is a DIAMOND!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And it's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Keep your envious little eyes off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I found it and it's mine,\Nfair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:48.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Okay, I can do this. I can…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.73,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Butterflies? Wait! Don't leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:01.85,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:06.35,Discord,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've been left behind\Nby your so-called friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:11.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm certain they're\Ndoing their best to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:15.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, it must be so upsetting to know how\Nweak and helpless they think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} weak and helpless and\NI appreciate their understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:23.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes, well… surely it burns you up, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.29,Discord,,0,0,0,,…that they're always\Npointing out your flaws, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.76,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Not really. In fact…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:33.71,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I think I'm awfully lucky to have friends\Nwho want me to be the best I can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.72,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, for goodness's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.44,Discord,,0,0,0,,You've been kind for\Nfar too long, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.44,Discord,,0,0,0,,Time to be cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.20,Discord,,0,0,0,,Arrivederci!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:49.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! I'm so glad\Nto see your friendly face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This awful labyrinth is\Ngetting to everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, boo hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:00.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Why don't you wave your magic little horn\Nand make everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:05.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. You can't.\NYou don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What is happening to my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And what are YOU laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Chocolate milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Little help here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,-But don't get any ideas about my gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,-You're welcome…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I know where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:36.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've got you now, Element.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:45.03,Discord,,0,0,0,,I can see why you like these\Nclouds so much. Very plush.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:48.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Get off there and put 'em up!\NC'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:51.36,Discord,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm here to deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've got a message for you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.95,Discord,,0,0,0,,Listen closely. This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:20:00.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,A weighty choice is yours to make ‒\NThe right selection or a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:05.94,Discord,,0,0,0,,If the wrong choice you choose to pursue,\NThe foundations of home will crumble without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:13.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale? Crumble… without me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:21.19,Discord,,0,0,0,,That box contains your wings.\NYou can take them and leave the game…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:26.29,Discord,,0,0,0,,…or you can carry on aimlessly\Nwandering this maze. Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:36.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Must… find… Rainbow Dash…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:40.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,As a team… we're unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:43.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash won't let us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, lookie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:48.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash is flyin' away.\NShe's abandonin' us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now I know that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How can it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:08.97,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well. Somepony broke\Nthe "no wings, no magic" rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.60,Discord,,0,0,0,,Game's over, my little ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.77,Discord,,0,0,0,,You didn't find your precious elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:23.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,Looks like we might be due\Nfor a big old storm of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:33.36,Somepony,,0,0,0,,To be continued…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:37.35,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon2anon\Nsunnysubs.com
